ates. In order to deal with\nthe bi-fluid system we generalize the almost compactness argument developed in\n\\cite{NovoPoko, Vasseur} to the case of time dependent domains with uniform\nH\\\"{o}lder continuous boundaries. Moreover, the proof of such a compactness\nresult depends on the existence of renormalized continuity equation in time\ndependent domains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2023 16:53:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2023 11:33:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-13"}
