 computational\napproach to the typically employed visual mode inspection technique and\nprovides a robust technique for analyzing the elastic wave response of periodic\nsolid media.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2023 19:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-30"}
