en up an opportunity not only for 1)\nenabling quicker prototyping of parallel/asynchrony-aware quantum-classical\nalgorithms on quantum circuit simulators in the short-term, but also for 2)\nrealizing a generic heterogeneous parallel programming model for\nquantum-classical heterogeneous platforms in the long-term.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2023 06:48:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2023 03:35:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-17"}
