 frameworks and outlines the essential characteristics of a concrete\nand connected framework AI risk assessment (C$^2$AIRA) framework. Our findings\nand insights can help relevant stakeholders choose suitable AI risk assessment\nframeworks and guide the design of future frameworks towards concreteness and\nconnectedness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2023 09:34:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2023 08:58:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 23 Mar 2023 13:35:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 24 May 2023 00:35:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-25"}
