 the new notions of suspensions over\nparallelizable Manifolds, and of twisted hyperelliptic Manifolds, and describe\nthe known results under the K\\\"ahler assumption.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2023 14:43:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-30"}
